OL,5, The International Handball Federation  
OL,6, (IHF) has changed its uniform rules    
OL,7, after it was criticised for requiring  
OL,8, female beach players to wear bikinis.  
OL,10,FThe governing authority had been under 
OL,11,Fpressure since a row over its dress    
OL,12,Fcode erupted at the European           
OL,13,Fchampionships in July.                 
OL,15,FNorway's female team were fined 1,500  
OL,16,Feuros (#1,269; $1,737) after their     
OL,17,Fplayers wore shorts instead of bikini  
OL,18,Fbottoms.                               
OL,20,FThe fine was branded sexist and led to 
OL,21,Fcalls to scrap mandatory clothing.     
